---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Timeline from "../components/Timeline.astro";
import GitHubIcon from "../components/GitHubIcon.astro";
import { SITE } from "../site.config";
---

<Layout title={`About | ${SITE.name}`}>
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto space-y-12">
        <section>
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
                About Me
            </h1>
            <div class="prose prose-zinc dark:prose-invert">
                <p
                    class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed mb-4"
                >
                    I am a software engineer and researcher targeting the <strong
                        >Class of 2027</strong
                    >. My passion lies in dissecting complex systems and
                    rebuilding them with better efficiency and design.
                </p>
                <p
                    class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed mb-4"
                >
                    It began in <strong>2018</strong> with a single line of Python.
                    By <strong>2021</strong>, I was integrating code with
                    hardware, competing in the <em
                        >Beijing Robotics Competition</em
                    > with custom Arduino implementations. This engineering rigor
                    carried into <strong>2023</strong> at the <em
                        >Jinpeng Sci-Tech Forum</em
                    >.
                </p>
                <p
                    class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed mb-4"
                >
                    Recently, I've shifted focus to solving tangible problems.
                    In <strong>2024</strong>, I engineered a Python-based data
                    analysis system to automate business intelligence for <strong
                        >my family's business</strong
                    >. In <strong>2025</strong>, I expanded into mobile
                    development, launching <strong>NightGuard</strong> on the App
                    Store. I also actively engaged with the industry by attending
                    the <em>Vivo Developer Conference</em>, while simultaneously
                    working on experimental Computer Vision research.
                </p>
                <p
                    class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed mb-4"
                >
                    In <strong>2026</strong>, I expanded from building products
                    to building communities. I co-founded <strong>Cobay</strong>,
                    where I organize offline founder meetups and lead development
                    of the website and community product. I also continued
                    exploring the wider builder ecosystem through <em
                        >AWS Summit China</em
                    > and <em>Cafe Cursor Beijing</em>.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
                Tech Stack
            </h2>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-indigo-500"></span>
                <strong>Languages:</strong> Swift, Python, Java, Rust, SQL
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-indigo-500"></span>
                <strong>Frameworks:</strong> SwiftUI, PyTorch, Astro, Spring Boot
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-indigo-500"></span>
                <strong>Tools:</strong> Git, Docker, VS Code, Xcode, Cursor
            </li>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-8">
                Journey
            </h2>
            <Timeline />
        </section>

        <section class="border-t border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800 pt-8">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
                Connect
            </h2>
            <div class="flex gap-4">
                <a
                    href={SITE.github}
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg bg-zinc-900 dark:bg-zinc-800 text-white dark:text-zinc-200 font-medium hover:bg-zinc-800 dark:hover:bg-zinc-700 transition-colors"
                    aria-label="GitHub"
                >
                    <GitHubIcon size={18} />
                    GitHub
                </a>
            </div>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-500">
                Contact me via <a
                    href={`mailto:${SITE.email}`}
                    class="text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 hover:text-indigo-500 dark:hover:text-indigo-300 transition-colors"
                    >{SITE.email}</a
                >
            </p>
        </section>
    </div>
</Layout>
